### 1. Listar todas las propiedades (p√∫blico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties

### 2. Crear propiedad (requiere ser HOST)
# @name createProperty
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beautiful Beach House",
  "description": "Amazing ocean view with private beach access",
  "price": 250,
  "maxGuests": 6,
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "bathrooms": 2,
  "propertyType": "HOUSE",
  "address": "123 Beach Road",
  "city": "Miami",
  "state": "FL",
  "country": "USA",
  "zipCode": "33139",
  "latitude": 25.7617,
  "longitude": -80.1918,
  "amenities": ["WiFi", "Pool", "Beach Access", "BBQ"],
  "images": ["beach1.jpg", "beach2.jpg", "beach3.jpg"]
}

### 3. Obtener detalle de la propiedad creada
@propertyId = {{createProperty.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}

### 4. Publicar la propiedad
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Listar propiedades publicadas
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties

### 6. Buscar por ciudad
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?city=Miami

### 7. Actualizar propiedad
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Luxury Beach House - Updated",
  "price": 300
}

### 8. Eliminar propiedad (descomentar cuando quieras probar)
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}